{"ID":"20220721143654-jqwvj55","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20220721143654-jqwvj55","title":"Java问题汇总","type":"doc","updated":"20221018163822"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220618211512-t3t99x4","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220618211512-t3t99x4","updated":"20220618211512"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"print输出单双引号问题"}]},{"ID":"20220618211513-a3kfcp2","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220618211513-a3kfcp2","updated":"20220618211513"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e"},{"ID":"20220618211514-cuqynhr","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20220618211514-cuqynhr","updated":"20220618211514"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"System.out.println(a+\"+\"+b+\"=\");\n这个里面一定要写双引号不能单引号\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]}]},{"ID":"20220618211515-evv6743","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220618211515-evv6743","updated":"20220618211515"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如何获取二维数组的行和列的个数"}]},{"ID":"20220618211516-ofnlcso","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20220618211516-ofnlcso","updated":"20220618211516"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"二维数组定义：int array[][]=new int[3][3];\n\n获取行长度 : int rowlength=array.length;\n\n获取列长度:int colength=array[0].length;\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]},{"ID":"20220618211528-qzfrhpq","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220618211528-qzfrhpq","updated":"20220618211528"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如何把字符串完整输出"}]},{"ID":"20220618211529-2zn1oej","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"202206182115